        OFFSET @__p_6 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_7 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t42] ON [x.BillDetails6].[BillId] = [t42].[Id]
) AS [t43] ON [dtoBillDetail.Product.WholePrices0].[ProductId] = [t43].[Id1]

""SELECT CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [Functions] AS [f]
        INNER JOIN [Permissions] AS [p] ON [f].[Id] = [p].[FunctionId]

        INNER JOIN [AppRoles] AS [r] ON [p].[RoleId] = [r].[Id]

END" (0723d8ff)
